Utterance.UttText: In room 2 is Ross Brighty, 81 years old under Dr Ben.
He came in for lung surgery and on the background of lung cancer 5 yrs ago and worsening asthma.
He had a scarring from the previous operation that needs to be operated again.
He is a new admission and he still need some admission paperworks sorted and assessments to be done.
The doctor hasn't seen him yet and still for review.
He is otherwise stable and obs within normal limits.
He is on a diabetic diet and for BGL BD on oral hypoglycaemic.
